DEPENDENCIES
------------

+ eBox components

	+ ebox

+ Debian packages (apt-get install <package>)
	
	+ openswan

+ Others:

	+ an IPSec enabled Linux kernel

INSTALLATION
------------

- Once all dependencies are satisfied, type:
	
	./configure
	make install

  configure will autodetect eBox base path to install

- You should not run openswan automatically on startup, this module will start
  it whenever it's needed:

  mv /etc/rcX.d/SXXipsec /etc/rcX.d/KXXipsec

  (replace the X's with the correct numbers)
